1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 d6 4. c3 Bd7 5. O-O Nf6 6. Re1 a6 7. Bf1 Bg4 8. h3
Bxf3 (8... Bh5 $2 {used to be the main line but is almost lost for Black after}
9. g4 Bg6 10. d4 $1 $16) 9. Qxf3 e6 {This the best Black can do.} {White has
several good options, giving him a small advantage. Take your pick!} 10. d3 (
10. Qg3 $5) (10. Na3 $5) 10... Be7 11. Qg3 (11. Bf4 $5) 11... O-O 12. Bh6 Ne8
13. Be3 d5 14. e5 $2 {After this mistake the advantage passes to Black!} ({
White should have played} 14. exd5 $1 exd5 15. Nd2 Nc7 (15... d4 16. cxd4 cxd4
17. Bf4 Nf6 {Our light-squared bishop will soon be the superstar in the
position:} 18. Be2 $16 {[%csl Ge2][%cal Ye2f3]}) 16. Nf3 Bd6 17. Qg4 f5 18. Qa4
$14) 14... f6 $15 (14... Qb6 $1 $15) 15. d4 cxd4 16. cxd4 fxe5 17. dxe5 d4 18.
Bf4 Nc7 19. Nd2 Bh4 20. Qh2 Rxf4 21. Qxf4 Bg5 22. Qe4 Bxd2 23. Bd3 g6 24. Re2
Bh6 25. Rf1 Qe7 26. f4 Nd5 27. g4 Bxf4 28. Rxf4 Nxf4 29. Qxf4 Rf8 30. Qg3 Qc5
31. Kh2 Qc1 32. Be4 Qd1 33. Rf2 Rxf2+ 34. Qxf2 Nxe5 35. Bxb7 d3 36. Bxa6 d2 37.
Qf6 Nf3+ 38. Kg3 Qg1+ 39. Kf4 Qd4+ 0-1

