is another passive and bad move. Black has two promising ways to play:} Rc8 $1
{Now it's too late for d4.} (9... c4 $1 {If the pawn on c4 is well protected -
as in this position - Black gets a good position.} 10. d4 cxd3 $132) 10. d3 g6
11. Nbd2 Bg7 12. Nf1 O-O 13. Ng3 e5 $15) 9... e5 10. Nbd2 g6 (10... Be7 11. Nf1
