{[%evp 0,9,16,16,53,52,79,44,76,24,24,-17]} 1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 d6 3. Bb5+ Nd7 4.
c3 {After having examined the line with 4.d4, we are going to study 4.c3 with
the idea of building a pawn centre with d4. After} Ngf6 {we return with the
bishop} 5. Bd3 {, planning Bc2-d4. The loss of time by moving the bishop
several times is justified by the passive position of the d7-knight.} *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
[Round "?"]
[White "THEORETICAL OVERVIEW"]
