cxd5 Qb6 19. dxc6 bxc6 20. Bc3 {White has achieved a permanent advantage due
to Black's weakened pawn structure.} Bf6 21. e5 Rce8 22. Qd1 Be7 23. exd6 Bf6
24. Bxf6 Nxf6 25. Ne5 c5 26. Qd3 Rd8 27. Rfd1 h5 28. h3 Rfe8 29. Qc4 Re6 30. d7
